name: "what will i become?"
description:
*THIS IS A NON-CANON SPIN-OFF OF GODH GIRL*

GODH GIRL journey started from inside a lab, cultured inside a fluid pod.

Is she human? A lab-grown human? Or nothing more than just a soul-less shell?

But now she is already living among us. If you have never realized this, then I suggest you to start looking.

Or...
perhaps...
you...

are the clone?
